name: M’isolo E Vivo
description: I isolate myself and live in solitude. Those are the words of William Barrety written on the walls of Villa Isola. This art deco style building is located in the city of Bandung, built in 1933 by a Dutch architect, Wolff Schoemaker. I am quite close to this building, because this building is also the rector's office where I study.
